query: SELECT DISTINCT bf.eventoId, f.turmaId, t.codigo as turmaCodigo FROM briefing_formando bf INNER JOIN formandos f ON bf.formandoId = f.id INNER JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id ORDER BY bf.eventoId;
